Aad u fiican. Domain-kaaga waa cabdul.page.gd, database-na waa Supabase.
Hadda samee talaabooyinkan si toos ah:

Ka qaado Supabase connection string

Gal Supabase project

Tag Project Settings > Database

Nuqul URI-ga Postgres (Transaction mode ama Session mode)

Ku xiro Vercel project-ka

Fur terminal:
cd D:\net\mysite

Login:
vercel login

Link project:
vercel link

Ku dar env vars production ee Vercel

vercel env add DJANGO_DEBUG production
qiime: false

vercel env add DJANGO_SECRET_KEY production
qiime: secret adag

vercel env add DJANGO_ALLOWED_HOSTS production
qiime: .vercel.app,cabdul.page.gd

vercel env add DJANGO_CSRF_TRUSTED_ORIGINS production
qiime: https://cabdul.page.gd,https://YOUR-PROJECT.vercel.app

vercel env add DJANGO_FORCE_HTTPS production
qiime: true

vercel env add DATABASE_URL production
qiime: Supabase Postgres URL

Mari migrations adigoo isticmaalaya Supabase URL

PowerShell:
$env:DATABASE_URL="PASTE_SUPABASE_URL"
python.exe manage.py migrate

Haddii aad rabto superuser:
python.exe manage.py createsuperuser

Deploy production

vercel --prod

Ku xiro domain-ka cabdul.page.gd

vercel domains add cabdul.page.gd

Vercel wuxuu ku siinayaa DNS record; ku dar DNS-ka page.gd sida uu ku farayo.

Sug propagation kadib fur:
https://cabdul.page.gd